data.name: infoIconFFmpegMode.ToolTip
data.value:
This changes the options in the FFMPEG command that is used to combine the images into the GIF. Most of the time use Mode 1.
Mode 1 should be better when dealing with transparency, but seems to have occasional issues with creating the GIF too small
Mode 2 should work if Mode 1 doesn't, but it doesn't work very well with transparency.
